{"tid":1080229,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Sharp 摺疊屏幕手機設計曝光","createTime":"2019-03-27T12:45:30.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T02:12:13.000Z","uid":50534,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4e1aa2eda27adbab2de4bdc7dc5f6f662dbca84c","tid":1080229,"uid":50534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-27T12:45:30.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://qooah.com/2019/03/27/sharp-folding-screen-phone-design-exposure/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2F2019%2F03%2F27%2Fsharp-folding-screen-phone-design-exposure%2F&d=5mmA4sQKuQaI7%2FjJJ4WTlxd7csCxFA%2BgjFQ0bWg4u80%3D&h=2ade1d27\" target=\"_blank\">https://qooah.com/2019/03/27/sharp-folding-screen-phone-design-exposure/</a><br />\n隨著柔宇、Samsung、華為的摺疊屏幕手機陸續發布，許多廠商不甘落後，鬥爭先恐後的發表主家的摺疊屏幕概念機，例如 LG、Motorola、聯想、小米、OPPO。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外， Sharp 似乎有有些動靜。雖然 Sharp 在兩年前收縮了手機的業務，戰略重心主要放在了歐洲市場，像是去年推出的 Aquos D10，C10 和 B10。<br />\n<br />\n根據 Sharp 在2017年向世界知識產權局（WIPO）提交，近日獲得審批接納的技術專利，中看到了專利圖片應該是類似於 MOTO Razr 的翻蓋設計。我們從外媒 LetsGoDigital 基於專利描述的插圖進行3D渲染後的照片，了解到 Sharp 的摺疊手機沒有劉海，邊框非常窄，沒有打孔。<br />\n<br />\n摺疊方面， Sharp 採用了獨特的鉸鏈設計，讓手機可以 2個位置的摺疊。可以選擇完全摺疊保護屏幕或者合上後留下部分屏幕空間。機身背面則是當鏡加閃關燈的組合。<br />\n<br />\n除此之外， Sharp 的可摺疊智能手機底部有一個接口，可以進行手機充電。機身左側還有三個按鈕，可能為音量鍵和電源鍵。<br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1231212231231321123.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F1231212231231321123.jpg&h=a9bda3de&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/1211232332.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F1211232332.jpg&h=872d17a8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://qooah.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/03/23213213.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fqooah.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2F23213213.jpg&h=b48b81a9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0cbb762f1a2a780